criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Patients with confirmed brain glioma, nasopharyngeal carcinoma, lung cancer,
             esophageal cancer, gastric cancer, liver cancer, prostate cancer, cervical cancer and
             rectal cancer;

          2. The medical imaging data (CT) of the subjects were complete and available;

          3. Between 18 and 75 years old, regardless of gender;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. The patients had metal implants;

          2. Not suitable for clinical trials judged by investigators.
